{"id":91862,"title":"Road accidents: a third burden of 'disease' in sub-Saharan Africa.","abstract":"Road traffic injuries (RTIs) continue to be a major cause of death and disability throughout low- and middle-income countries (LMICs). The aim of this commentary is highlight some of the major causes of RTIs in sub-Saharan Africa and suggests strategies for better road safety as well as suggestions on how to reduce road accidents in LMICs.","date":"2014-01-28","categories":"Wounds and Injuries","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24469303","annotations":[{"name":"Traffic collision","weight":0.801843,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Traffic_collision"},{"name":"Disease","weight":0.653635,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disease"},{"name":"Death","weight":0.621852,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Death"},{"name":"Traffic","weight":0.592413,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Traffic"},{"name":"Disability","weight":0.574262,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disability"},{"name":"Road traffic safety","weight":0.520829,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Road_traffic_safety"},{"name":"Road","weight":0.499321,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Road"},{"name":"Accident","weight":0.481682,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Accident"},{"name":"Safety","weight":0.451825,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Safety"},{"name":"Country","weight":0.370748,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Country"},{"name":"List of causes of death by rate","weight":0.347082,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_causes_of_death_by_rate"},{"name":"Strategy","weight":0.182524,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strategy"},{"name":"Africa","weight":0.149429,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Africa"},{"name":"Major","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wi